mainwidget.cpp, mainwidget.h:
    Class definition and implementation for the application widget.
    All glue between interface and HoughDetector/TemplateMatcher lives here.
    Also has helpers to get a subimage and calculate calibration.

hough.cpp, hough.h:
    Definition and implementation of HoughDetector, which is the class, that
    performs hough transformation.
    Implemented using openCV.

template.cpp, template.h:
    Definition and implementation of TemplateMatcher, which is the class that
    handles matching of templates.
    Implemented using openCV.

videoframe.cpp, videoframe.h:
    Definition and implementation of the video widget.

subimage.cpp, subimage.h:
    Definition and implementation of Subimage, which is the class, that is used
    to store only parts of a video frame. Converts between cv::Mat and QImage
    and stores offset in the original frame.
